Package tech.gitpicard.jcalc

Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.gitpicard.jcalc.Parser
  • public final class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds an abstract syntax tree from a lexer that will feed the parser tokens. The abstract syntax tree can be directly evaluated by the calculator.

    • Constructor Summary
